[
  {
    "id": "thermal-tab",
    "type": "tab",
    "label": "Thermal Tanks",
    "disabled": false,
    "info": "Thermal tank Supervisor dashboard v0.4.0\n\nPOST endpoint:   /thermal/ingest  (pushed by the thermal-analyzer container)\nThermal API:     flow.thermal_base (default resolved from hostname, override with THERMAL_API)\n\nGroups:\n  • Overview       — site header + deep link to operator console (:8080)\n  • Tanks          — per-tank KPI cards (level, ft, bbl, rate, ETA)\n  • Trends         — 24 h level & temperature history (high-confidence only)\n  • Alerts         — persisted out-of-band history (bounded 200 rows)\n  • Events         — raw ingest log (collapsed)\n\nBreaking changes vs v0.3:\n  • `ts` is ALWAYS milliseconds (publisher guarantees). No unit math.\n  • Iframe removed. Live stream lives at the operator console, not in NR.\n  • Per-tank KPI cards replace the single ui_gauge (which collapsed multi-topic).\n  • Handles new payload fields: `reading`, `geometry`, `calibration`, `medium_confidence`, `site_id`.\n"
  },
